item.title: CVE-2021-21666|2024-08-03T18:23:27.488Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20kiuwan%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Kiuwan Plugin 1.6.0 and earlier does not escape query parameters in an error message for a form validation endpoint, resulting in a reflected cross-site scripting (XSS) vulnerability.
